name: US01
text: How would you rate the level of difficulty to use the tool?

name: US2
text: How would you rate the level of difficulty to understand the graphs provided by the tool?

name: US3
text: Is it easy to navigate within the displayed graph to find features/understand the design of the analysed system?

name: US4
text: Looking into the graphs/lattices built from each system, can you assign each system a design quality score (1 for the system having the highest number of refactoring opportunities, and 4 for the system having the smallest number of refactoring opportunities)
